Description: Wola SDK
        ========
        
        |Build Status|
        
        Python SDK for Wola GraphQL
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install from Github.
        
        .. code:: sh
        
            pip install git+https://github.com/WolaApplication/wola-sdk
        
        
        Quick start
        -----------
        
        **Client**
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> import wola_sdk
            >>> client = wola_sdk.WolaGql(
            ...     url='https://gql.waveapplication.com',
            ...     token='my-token')
        
        
        **Get node**
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> query = '''
            ... {
            ...   waves(duration_Gte: "30:00") {
            ...     edges {
            ...       node {
            ...         id
            ...         duration
            ...       }
            ...     }
            ...   }
            ... }
            ... '''
            >>> client.execute(query)
        
        **Response**
        
        .. code:: graphql
        
            {
              "data": {
                "waves": {
                  "edges": [
                    {
                      "node": {
                        "id": "V2F2ZU5vZGU6Mg==",
                        "duration": "0:45:00"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
        
        **Exception handler**
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> try:
            ...     client.execute(query)
            ... except wola_sdk.WolaGqlError as err:
            ...     print(err.message)
        
        
        Tests
        -----
        
        .. code:: sh
        
            make test
        
        
